Team challenge 09:
What program are we going to create?
We will create a very light version of Super Smash Brothers. Two players will choose from a small roster of characters, and fight to the last man standing in a simplified SSB style
What technologies will we use?
We will be using sample projects from Arcade and modify them into our own.
What features will we include?
We will include one on one fighting. Four players to choose from. They will have classes that have life bar, attacks, jumping, movement, and a stage.
What is your timeline?
We will have an alpha version done by Thursday the 25 of March, and have the final version done by Tuesday the 6 of April
